title: Dogs and All About Them
creator: Robert Leighton
description: Librivox recording of Dogs and All About Them by Robert Leighton. Read by LibriVox Volunteers. This comprehensive guide on dog-rearing looks at dogs as more than just pets - as people's best friends. The author describes each breed of dog in a detailed and systematic way, with complete notes on show-dogs. (Summary by Diana Majlinger) For more free audiobooks, or to become a volunteer reader, please visit librivox.org. Download M4B Part 1 (199MB) Download M4B Part 2 (175MB)
